<bibRefCitation id="4D26F5937442BF56CF2CFFD3FAB5FC3C" author="Osten" box="[1048,1284,901,926]" pageId="10" pageNumber="65" refString="Osten Sacken, C. R. (1877) Western Diptera: descriptions of new genera and species of Diptera from the region west of the Mississippi, and especially from California. Bulletin of the United States Geological Survey of the Territories, 3, 189 - 354. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 57939" type="journal article" year="1877">Osten Sacken, 1877</bibRefCitation>
