</taxonomicName>
was later transferred by 
<bibRefCitation id="4D26F5937442BF56CB8EFFA4FEC2FBA8" author="Evenhuis" box="[186,371,1009,1034]" pageId="10" pageNumber="65" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. (1986) The genera of the Phthiriinae of Australia and the New World. Published by the author, Honolulu, 57 pp." type="book" year="1986">Evenhuis (1986)</bibRefCitation>
